Code preview of table Region

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('REGION')
and type = 'U')
drop table REGION
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: REGION */
/*==============================================================*/
create table REGION (
REG_IDENTIFIKATOR int not null,
TR_OZNAKA char(1) null,
DR_IDENTIFIKATOR char(3) null,
NAS_DR_IDENTIFIKATOR char(3) null,
NM_IDENTIFIKATOR int null,
OP_OZNAKA numeric(3,0) null,
REG_NAZIV varchar(80) not null,
constraint PK_REGION primary key nonclustered (REG_IDENTIFIKATOR)
)
go
